@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="privacy-container">

    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("dd.MM.yyyy")</p>

    <p>
        TalkGear (“we”, “us”, “our”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our website and services.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Scope</h2>
    <p>
        This policy applies to all users of TalkGear’s website, platform, and services.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Name and email address</li>
        <li>Account details (if you register)</li>
        <li>Messages or content you share</li>
        <li>Usage data (pages visited, time spent)</li>
        <li>Device and browser information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
        <li>To communicate with you</li>
        <li>To personalize user experience</li>
        <li>To analyze performance and usage</li>
        <li>To ensure security and prevent misuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
        We use cookies to improve your experience, analyze traffic, and remember preferences.
        You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        We do not sell your personal data. We may share information with trusted third-party services
        (such as hosting or analytics providers) only when necessary to operate our platform.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>
        Your data may be stored within or outside the EU/EEA. We ensure that all transfers comply with applicable data protection laws.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
        We retain your data only as long as necessary for providing our services and fulfilling legal obligations.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Security</h2>
    <p>
        We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data.
        However, no system is completely secure.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data.
        You may also withdraw consent where applicable.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions about this policy, contact us:
        <br />
        <strong>Email:</strong> mehdi-sultani@hotmail.com
    </p>

</div>